Q1

麥當勞 台北館前店

MIC.buffer <- gBuffer(MIC, byid = TRUE, id = MIC$ID, width = 1000);
chainDensity <- poly.counts(MIC, MIC.buffer);
chainDensityMax <- subset(MIC, MIC$ID == as.numeric(names(which.max(chainDensity))));
chainDensityMax.buffer <- gBuffer(chainDensityMax, width = 1000);

par(family = "BiauKai");
par(mar = c(1, 0, 1.5, 0));
plot(Taipei_Vill);
plot(FastFood, add = TRUE, pch = 20, col = "blue");
plot(chainDensityMax, add = TRUE, pch = 20, col = "red");
plot(chainDensityMax.buffer, add = TRUE, border = "red");
text(x = chainDensityMax$X_COOR, y = chainDensityMax$Y_COOR, chainDensityMax$ALIAS, pos = 2, col = "darkgreen");

Q2

台北市 中山區 正得里

centroids <- gCentroid(Taipei_Vill, byid = TRUE, id = Taipei_Vill$V_ID);
distances <- gWithinDistance(centroids, MIC, byid = TRUE, dist = 1000);
mostCoveredVillage <- subset(Taipei_Vill, Taipei_Vill$V_ID == names(which.max(apply(distances, 2, sum))));
nearbyMIC <- distances[, names(which.max(apply(distances, 2, sum)))];

par(family = "BiauKai");
par(mar = c(1, 0, 1.5, 0));
plot(Taipei_Vill);
plot(MIC[nearbyMIC,], add = TRUE, col = "blue", pch = 20);
plot(mostCoveredVillage, add = TRUE, col = "red");
text(x = centroids[names(which.max(apply(distances, 2, sum)))]$x, y = centroids[names(which.max(apply(distances, 2, sum)))]$y, mostCoveredVillage$VILLAGE, pos = 2, col = "darkgreen");
